      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not about small steps anymore. i've tried the small steps, the big steps, the \"different approaches.\" it's the same thing every time. the cycle just restarts. it feels more like a trap than a pattern. i'm just waiting for the next time everything breaks again. it feels inevitable.",
